+/*
+ * FireDTV driver (formerly known as FireSAT)
+ *
+ * Copyright (C) 2004 Andreas Monitzer <andy@monitzer.com>
+ * Copyright (C) 2007-2008 Ben Backx <ben@bbackx.com>
